          "reviewBody": "Disappointing Experience at Army Public School Bhopal\n\n- Went there as a visitor and had to wait for 2-3 hours to meet the principal\n- No receptionist to greet or assist\n- Office staff showed no respect in communication\n- Overall the management is pathetic\n\nAvoid getting your child admitted here. Worst school in Bhopal .",
