          "reviewBody": "APS Bhopal is treating students so bad that they are not providing TC on time saying technical issues.And that has to be sorted out at their end rather than creating issues for the students.It's delaying admission in APS at presently posted place.They are least bothered about this.Also if any such difficulty is there other APS are issuing manually prepared TCs to students.That too APS Bhopal is denying without any proper reason.Its adversely affecting kids' studies who had to leave Bhopal on getting transferred to a new place.They told us to wait for 10 days and now saying again to wait for 10 more days.Without TC no other APS will give admission also.That means students have to sit at home skipping all the classes approx for one month simply because APS Bhopal is not taking any effort to resolve the issue.What parents can do in this scenario??",
